This project is a calculator that will calc, the letive days, the useful days, and the number of classes the student may miss 
according the University of Bras√≠lia abscence policy, which determines that the student has to have 75% presence in classroom.
The number of abscencs is calculated by the number of classes ministreds, which is 25% of it.
The calculator isn't perfectly, since there are exception, as strikes, abscence of professors, and others.
